The project will include:

* Modern glassmorphism UI
* GPT5 Mini branding
* Automatic GitHub repository discovery
* Manual + GitHub data merge
* Intelligent search
* Dashboard analytics
* Repository statistics
* Project cards
* Domain manager
* Infrastructure monitor
* Dark/Light themes
* PWA support
* Offline cache
* GitHub Actions deployment
* GitHub Pages deployment
* Netlify deployment
* Vercel deployment
* SEO optimization
* Responsive mobile interface
* Animations
* Markdown README viewer
* Repository language charts
* Last commit information
* Star and fork counters
* Automatic refresh

Because this is a large project (roughly 8,000вЂ“15,000 lines of code), it cannot fit into a single ChatGPT response.

The best approach is to generate it as a complete downloadable project, with every HTML, CSS, JavaScript, configuration file, GitHub Actions workflow, and PWA asset already organized. That way you can clone it, deploy it immediately, and continue extending it as your Web4 ecosystem grows.
